                "html": "<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; font-weight: bold; display: block;\"># 格斗运动中的感知认知专业知识：从科学研究到训练</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">## 1. 引言</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">格斗运动的表现</strong> 通常从生理学、人体测量学或生物力学的角度进行广泛研究。通常，格斗运动的<strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">条件训练</strong> 依赖于生理学研究，而技术则从生物力学角度进行评估。然而，<strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">格斗运动专家</strong> 和新手在心理特征上也存在显著差异。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">训练中的挑战：</strong></p> \n<ul data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    训练通常依赖于教练的经验，而不是科学研究。 \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    因此，本文的目的是通过综述相关的<strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">科学文献</strong>，探讨格斗运动中的感知认知变量，并为训练提供指导。 \n  </section></li> \n</ul> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">## 2. 感知认知专业知识的研究</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">科学研究成果：</strong></p> \n<ul data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    在拳击、击剑、空手道和跆拳道等格斗运动中，反应时间（RT）的研究结果不一致。专家的反应时间可能较短，但一些研究表明反应时间并不是比赛成功的预测因素（Martinez de Quel 等, 2015）。 \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    专家展示了优秀的<strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">预判能力</strong>，能够在攻击的最初时刻识别对手的攻击（Rosalie &amp; Muller, 2013）。 \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    专家的视觉行为，如将目光固定在对手的躯干和头部，起到了<strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">视觉枢轴</strong> 的作用，使得他们能够及时捕捉到所需信息以做出适当的反应（Ripoll 等, 1995）。 \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n    这种优势与专家对<strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">情景概率</strong> 的熟知密切相关，这种知识有助于战术训练（Milazzo 等, 2015）。 \n  </section></li> \n</ul> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(19, 92, 224); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">## 3. 应用于训练</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">训练建议：</strong></p> \n<ol data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"> <strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">耦合感知与行动：</strong> 训练应该尽量模拟比赛的实际约束条件，例如进行比赛、对抗练习、攻击防御练习，或使用液晶眼镜等设备。 \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"> <strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">防守者的训练：</strong> \n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n    <li> \n     <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n       将目光固定在对手的身体中心（头部和躯干）。 \n     </section></li> \n    <li> \n     <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n       通过对对手身体动作、战场环境（得分、比赛时间、对手常用技术等）的观察，推测对手的下一步动作。 \n     </section></li> \n    <li> \n     <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n       调整与对手的距离，保持适当的<strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding-top: 4px; padding-bottom: 4px; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">起始姿势</strong>（如防守姿势）以快速反应。 \n     </section></li> \n    <li> \n     <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n       设计灵活的应对反应，适应可能的攻击变化，如通过向后撤步避免多种攻击。 \n     </section></li> \n   </ul> \n  </section></li> \n <li> \n  <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(1, 1, 1); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"> <strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 153, 210, 0.7) 0%, rgba(239, 189, 181, 0.7) 97.3%), none; background-orig